                    3. 李根芳。July 2005〈翻譯類暢銷書在台灣〉。第一屆海峽兩岸翻譯與跨文化交流研討會。北京：清華大學。 
                    4. Lee, Ken-fang.  July 2004. “The Project of Modernity and Lu Xun’s Translation of From the Earth  to the Moon.’ BCLA International Conference “Invention: Literature and  Science”. Leeds University,   England.

                    5. Lee,  Ken-fang. June 2004. “Heat and Dust: ‘The Trio’ in The Gobi Desert”
                    The Ninth Quadrennial  International Conference on Comparative Literature. “Some Like It Hot,  Others Don’t: Embodiment of Glocal Knowledge”.

                    6. 李根芳。June 2003。〈《血色花瓣》裡的異鄉人〉。發表於第廿七屆全國比較文學會議，東吳大學。 
                    7. 李根芳。Jan 2003。〈吳爾芙在台灣〉。發表於第七屆口筆譯教學研討會，輔仁大學。 
