                    9. Lee, Ken-fang.  July 2001. “Home and Away: Different Receptions of Ang Lee’s Crouching  Tiger, Hidden Dragon by Ang Lee.” Cultural Studies Between Politics and  Ethics: An International Interdisciplinary Conference, Bath Spa University College, U.K.

